prompt:
Patient: Hello?

Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Damian Benton?

Patient: Yes.

Nurse: Great, Mr. Benton. I'm calling on behalf of your primary care doctor, Doctor Marta Marcuso, to check in on you. How have you been doing lately?

Patient: Well, I think with all of my health issues, I'm doing pretty good, you know, considering

Nurse: I'm glad to hear that you're doing well, Mr. Benton. It's important to focus on the positive. Is there anything you're looking forward to doing this week?

Patient: Probably do a little Christmas baking.

responses.gpt4: That sounds delightful, Mr. Benton. Christmas baking can be quite the holiday tradition. What's your favorite thing to bake?
responses.our_model: That sounds like a lovely plan, Mr. Benton. Christmas baking can be such a joy. What kind of treats are you planning to make?
